[
  {
    "startTime": 9.792,
    "endTime": 13.292,
    "text": "[Ram Dass was not able to appear in person because of a stroke in 1997]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.292,
    "endTime": 16.304,
    "text": "[which prevents him from travel, and also affects his speech]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.304,
    "endTime": 18.464,
    "text": "[Ram Dass]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.464,
    "endTime": 24.595,
    "text": "[Cultivating Our Spiritual Heart]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.595,
    "endTime": 28.144,
    "text": "Namaste."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.144,
    "endTime": 31.070999999999998,
    "text": "My name is Ram Dass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.071,
    "endTime": 35.542,
    "text": "I'm sorry I can't be with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.542,
    "endTime": 37.016,
    "text": "I guess"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.016,
    "endTime": 46.232,
    "text": "we will communicate in this way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.232,
    "endTime": 54.01,
    "text": "I'd like to speak to you about the spiritual heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.01,
    "endTime": 60.86,
    "text": "The spiritual heart is not in time,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.86,
    "endTime": 64.667,
    "text": "nor is it in space."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.667,
    "endTime": 69.25,
    "text": "It's just being,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.25,
    "endTime": 82.251,
    "text": "and it's being present in this moment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.251,
    "endTime": 91.751,
    "text": "The spiritual heart is being here now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.751,
    "endTime": 98.69200000000001,
    "text": "The evolution of the spiritual heart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.692,
    "endTime": 106.17899999999999,
    "text": "is not a journey through time and space."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.179,
    "endTime": 113.751,
    "text": "It is flowering of presence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.751,
    "endTime": 117.02000000000001,
    "text": "There are fully conscious beings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.02,
    "endTime": 122.87599999999999,
    "text": "in history"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.876,
    "endTime": 130.725,
    "text": "who have identified"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.725,
    "endTime": 139.167,
    "text": "with that kind of presence,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.167,
    "endTime": 141.501,
    "text": "like Christ,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.501,
    "endTime": 144.811,
    "text": "like Buddha,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.811,
    "endTime": 147.55,
    "text": "and Mohammad,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.55,
    "endTime": 152.58,
    "text": "or Krishna."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.58,
    "endTime": 156.87,
    "text": "They don't appear in time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.87,
    "endTime": 167.122,
    "text": "They're always present."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.122,
    "endTime": 170.73100000000002,
    "text": "In our new book,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.731,
    "endTime": 176.666,
    "text": "called, \"Be Love Now,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.666,
    "endTime": 183.783,
    "text": "we use examples of Indian Saints"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.783,
    "endTime": 192.10199999999998,
    "text": "from the last century."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.102,
    "endTime": 199.86,
    "text": "And they represent the human potential."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.86,
    "endTime": 206.13400000000001,
    "text": "They show us what our potential is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.134,
    "endTime": 208.50099999999998,
    "text": "as human beings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.501,
    "endTime": 214.30100000000002,
    "text": "They also show"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.301,
    "endTime": 219.771,
    "text": "the oneness of humanity,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.771,
    "endTime": 227.069,
    "text": "and they show the way that love"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.069,
    "endTime": 229.19899999999998,
    "text": "brings us all together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.199,
    "endTime": 234.531,
    "text": "The presence of a realized being"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.531,
    "endTime": 241.601,
    "text": "shifts our awareness from ego - who we think we are -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.601,
    "endTime": 248.25,
    "text": "to soul - to who we really are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.25,
    "endTime": 254.31,
    "text": "Because the awareness in the heart,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.31,
    "endTime": 261.25,
    "text": "your awareness and mine, are one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.25,
    "endTime": 268.709,
    "text": "My own perception of world changed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.709,
    "endTime": 277.871,
    "text": "in 1966,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.871,
    "endTime": 289.68899999999996,
    "text": "when I first met my guru in India."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.689,
    "endTime": 291.25,
    "text": "Before meeting him,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.25,
    "endTime": 296.161,
    "text": "I was Richard Alpert,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.161,
    "endTime": 300.918,
    "text": "a social psychologist,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.918,
    "endTime": 304.752,
    "text": "a psychedelic explorer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.752,
    "endTime": 308.964,
    "text": "I had interviewed with him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.964,
    "endTime": 315.216,
    "text": "And afterwards, I was Ram Dass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.216,
    "endTime": 331.957,
    "text": "He changed my ego-centered to soul-centered."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.957,
    "endTime": 337.13599999999997,
    "text": "The way he did it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.136,
    "endTime": 343.25,
    "text": "first,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.25,
    "endTime": 348.584,
    "text": "he showed me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.584,
    "endTime": 355.959,
    "text": "he knew what I'm thinking,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.959,
    "endTime": 363.891,
    "text": "now and previously, which blew my mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.891,
    "endTime": 369.73,
    "text": "He unconditionally loved me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.73,
    "endTime": 374.851,
    "text": "And that changed me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.851,
    "endTime": 381.021,
    "text": "It was not his powers that changed me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.021,
    "endTime": 393.021,
    "text": "it was his love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.021,
    "endTime": 401.034,
    "text": "And his love - he was love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.034,
    "endTime": 403.584,
    "text": "He didn't love me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.584,
    "endTime": 410.13100000000003,
    "text": "he was love,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.131,
    "endTime": 412.08299999999997,
    "text": "a being of love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.083,
    "endTime": 421.834,
    "text": "When I was first in India"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.834,
    "endTime": 426.0,
    "text": "in the 60s,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.0,
    "endTime": 430.295,
    "text": "Maharajji said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.295,
    "endTime": 436.665,
    "text": "\"I'm blessing you for your book.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.665,
    "endTime": 444.47,
    "text": "And I had no book."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.47,
    "endTime": 448.86,
    "text": "So I said, \"What book are you talking about?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.86,
    "endTime": 458.70300000000003,
    "text": "And he didn't respond."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.703,
    "endTime": 469.82099999999997,
    "text": "The book I then wrote, \"Be Here Now,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.821,
    "endTime": 480.103,
    "text": "has sold probably over a million copies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.103,
    "endTime": 485.77,
    "text": "And so many people say that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485.77,
    "endTime": 498.459,
    "text": "that book changed them from ego to soul."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.459,
    "endTime": 503.082,
    "text": "One blessing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.082,
    "endTime": 515.253,
    "text": "It was his book."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.253,
    "endTime": 520.793,
    "text": "So, now I'm 80 years old,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.793,
    "endTime": 527.792,
    "text": "40 years after \"Be Here Now,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.792,
    "endTime": 533.178,
    "text": "and we have a new book,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 533.178,
    "endTime": 541.292,
    "text": "\"Be Love Now,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.292,
    "endTime": 549.8340000000001,
    "text": "in which I reconsider"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 549.834,
    "endTime": 557.967,
    "text": "my relation to Maharajji,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 557.967,
    "endTime": 564.057,
    "text": "and the love became central now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.057,
    "endTime": 569.414,
    "text": "Reading my mind"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.414,
    "endTime": 577.874,
    "text": "was the beginning of the ritual."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 577.874,
    "endTime": 583.292,
    "text": "After that, I said to myself,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 583.292,
    "endTime": 585.995,
    "text": "\"If he's reading my mind,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.995,
    "endTime": 590.531,
    "text": "he knows much more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 590.531,
    "endTime": 597.751,
    "text": "than anybody knows about me,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597.751,
    "endTime": 601.161,
    "text": "and I was embarrassed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.161,
    "endTime": 605.04,
    "text": "And I sat in front of him,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 605.04,
    "endTime": 608.635,
    "text": "and I was sitting on the grass,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.635,
    "endTime": 613.117,
    "text": "and I looked down at the grass"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.117,
    "endTime": 616.448,
    "text": "and I thought of all the things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.448,
    "endTime": 624.7379999999999,
    "text": "that I wouldn't want anybody to know about me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.738,
    "endTime": 634.335,
    "text": "because if they knew those things, they wouldn't love me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.335,
    "endTime": 638.5210000000001,
    "text": "And when I finished that list,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 638.521,
    "endTime": 644.151,
    "text": "I looked up and he was looking at me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.151,
    "endTime": 647.9399999999999,
    "text": "with unconditional love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.94,
    "endTime": 651.9200000000001,
    "text": "Unconditional love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.92,
    "endTime": 656.913,
    "text": "And I had never in my life,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656.913,
    "endTime": 662.184,
    "text": "in my life!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.184,
    "endTime": 666.2429999999999,
    "text": "experienced that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 666.243,
    "endTime": 675.267,
    "text": "One time, the second time I was in India,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.267,
    "endTime": 681.542,
    "text": "he motioned me over and he said, \"Do you know Gandhi?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 681.542,
    "endTime": 688.205,
    "text": "I said, \"I don't know him, I know of him.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 688.205,
    "endTime": 696.7900000000001,
    "text": "And he said, \"I want you to be like Gandhi.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.79,
    "endTime": 703.0,
    "text": "And I went to the bazaar"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.0,
    "endTime": 708.671,
    "text": "and I got those little glasses, the Gandhi glasses,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 708.671,
    "endTime": 711.481,
    "text": "but that didn't do the trick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 711.481,
    "endTime": 715.561,
    "text": "I just didn't feel like Gandhi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 715.561,
    "endTime": 724.0830000000001,
    "text": "Gandhi said, \"My life is my message.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.083,
    "endTime": 731.156,
    "text": "Maybe that was what Maharajji meant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 731.156,
    "endTime": 739.2349999999999,
    "text": "My life must be my message."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 739.235,
    "endTime": 748.7040000000001,
    "text": "And all of the great saints"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 748.704,
    "endTime": 753.7919999999999,
    "text": "could say, \"My life is my message.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 753.792,
    "endTime": 760.461,
    "text": "Maharajji gave me instructions:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 760.461,
    "endTime": 765.122,
    "text": "\"Ram Dass, tell the truth,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 765.122,
    "endTime": 769.459,
    "text": "and love everybody.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 769.459,
    "endTime": 779.1669999999999,
    "text": "\"Everybody, Maharajji? I can't do that.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 779.167,
    "endTime": 785.2800000000001,
    "text": "He said, nose to nose,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 785.28,
    "endTime": 789.61,
    "text": "\"Ram Dass, I want you to tell the truth,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 789.61,
    "endTime": 793.198,
    "text": "and love everybody.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 793.198,
    "endTime": 800.061,
    "text": "Most people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 800.061,
    "endTime": 804.091,
    "text": "want to get free of their suffering,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 804.091,
    "endTime": 808.901,
    "text": "and most people want that in their heart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 808.901,
    "endTime": 814.9699999999999,
    "text": "of love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 814.97,
    "endTime": 822.009,
    "text": "St. John of the Cross said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 822.009,
    "endTime": 827.371,
    "text": "\"I saw the river."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 827.371,
    "endTime": 830.372,
    "text": "Each soul must pass"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 830.372,
    "endTime": 836.762,
    "text": "in the name of that river -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 836.762,
    "endTime": 840.7049999999999,
    "text": "the river of suffering."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 840.705,
    "endTime": 846.643,
    "text": "And I saw the boat, which carries the soul"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 846.643,
    "endTime": 849.712,
    "text": "across that river."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 849.712,
    "endTime": 856.221,
    "text": "And the name of the boat was Love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 856.221,
    "endTime": 863.181,
    "text": "The evolution of the spiritual heart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 863.181,
    "endTime": 870.981,
    "text": "is not a journey through time and space,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 870.981,
    "endTime": 876.63,
    "text": "it is a flowering of presence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 876.63,
    "endTime": 883.472,
    "text": "God, guru, and self"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 883.472,
    "endTime": 890.228,
    "text": "are in your and my heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 890.228,
    "endTime": 893.443,
    "text": "They are in everybody's heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 893.443,
    "endTime": 899.8969999999999,
    "text": "So then you don't have to go to a distant land,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 899.897,
    "endTime": 905.2,
    "text": "you can go to the guru in your heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 905.2,
    "endTime": 914.354,
    "text": "That's what the human potential is: the heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 914.354,
    "endTime": 921.301,
    "text": "And what these saints represent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 921.301,
    "endTime": 929.1120000000001,
    "text": "are just that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 929.112,
    "endTime": 935.4939999999999,
    "text": "They represent our potential."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 935.494,
    "endTime": 940.974,
    "text": "I want to invite you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 940.974,
    "endTime": 948.154,
    "text": "to move your identity from ego to soul."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 948.154,
    "endTime": 954.145,
    "text": "For what each of us carries"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 954.145,
    "endTime": 962.631,
    "text": "in the spiritual heart"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 962.631,
    "endTime": 968.101,
    "text": "is loving awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 968.101,
    "endTime": 972.6,
    "text": "Loving awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 972.6,
    "endTime": 980.963,
    "text": "Awareness of everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 980.963,
    "endTime": 982.5419999999999,
    "text": "Loving awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 982.542,
    "endTime": 989.431,
    "text": "And that's what our spiritual heart is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 989.431,
    "endTime": 991.792,
    "text": "Get your awareness,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 991.792,
    "endTime": 1000.422,
    "text": "get your identity down to the heart,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1000.42,
    "endTime": 1005.588,
    "text": "the middle of the heart space,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1005.59,
    "endTime": 1012.08,
    "text": "just say, \"I am loving awareness.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1012.08,
    "endTime": 1015.89,
    "text": "I am loving awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1015.89,
    "endTime": 1021.771,
    "text": "I am loving awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1021.77,
    "endTime": 1027.629,
    "text": "(whispering) I am loving awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1027.63,
    "endTime": 1035.1090000000002,
    "text": "I am loving awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1035.11,
    "endTime": 1043.37,
    "text": "(whispering) I am loving awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1043.37,
    "endTime": 1053.37,
    "text": "Namaste."
  }
]